item.title: CVE-2018-1249|2024-09-17T03:19:03.618Z -- dell%20emc -- idrac9
item.description: Dell EMC iDRAC9 versions prior to 3.21.21.21 did not enforce the use of TLS/SSL for a connection to iDRAC web server for certain URLs. A man-in-the-middle attacker could use this vulnerability to strip the SSL/TLS protection from a connection between a client and a server.
